description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results (before fees and expenses) of the S-Network Composite Closed-End Fund IndexSM.
 The fund generally invests at least 90% of its total assets in securities of U.S.-listed closed-end funds that comprise the underlying index. It is a "fund of funds," as it invests its assets in the common shares of funds included in the underlying index rather than in individual securities (the "underlying funds").
